⁠

REVIEW: I've been a massive fan of The Secret for some years and have loosely used its teachings over the years. This book is full of REAL amazing and inspiring stories from REAL people from all over the world which is hugely uplifting to know that no matter where you are in the world or what your circumstances are you can use the teachings of The Secret to change your life. The book is not only full of stories but also inspiration quotes and key points in every section which you can refer back to at any time! I just love how the author makes the book personal to YOU the reader, as if the book has been solely written for you.⁠
It gave me great hope that I too can make small or big beautiful changes to my life one step at a time.⁠
📚⁠

And for lovers of The Secret⁠
